## Out of Scope

Deliberately excluded to maintain vanilla+ feel and scope:

- New taming items — vanilla items only
- Companion breeding
- Companion equipment or inventory
- Companion combat abilities
- GUI for companion stats
- Shoulder riding
- Any companion that is already tameable in vanilla (wolves, cats, horses, parrots, etc.)
- Hostile or neutral mobs (only passive mobs are in scope)

